==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Sagebrush
<hw>Sage"brush`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A low irregular
shrub (<spn>Artemisia tridentata</spn>), of the order
<ord>Compositae</ord>, covering vast tracts of the dry alkaline regions
of the American plains; -- called also <altname>sagebush</altname>, and
<altname>wild sage</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Sagebrush State</ent>⟦br⟧
